{"word":"G1239 - διαδίδωμι - diadídōmi - dee-ad-id'-o-mee - Distribute","slug":"G1239","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαδίδωμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diadídōmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-ad-id'-o-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Distribute"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B4;&#x03C9;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - diadido&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>dee-ad-id'-o-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G1325\">G1325</a>; to <i>give throughout</i> a crowd, that is, <i>deal out</i>; also to <i>deliver</i> over (as to a successor): - (make) distribute (-ion), divide, give."}]}